n of funicular railways, aerial cableways etc. This class excludes passenger transport by inter-urban railways, see 4911.','4931'),('49321','Jeepney and Uv Express Operation',NULL,'4932'),('49322','Tricycles and Pedicabs Operation',NULL,'4932'),('49323','Public Utility Cars and Taxicabs Operation',NULL,'4932'),('49324','Chartered Cars (Rent-a-car)',NULL,'4932'),('49325','Operations of Vehicles for Transportation Network Service (Ride-sharing Services)',NULL,'4932'),('49326','Public Utility Electric Vehicle (Ev) Operation such as Plug-in Electric Vehicle (Pev), Battery Electric Vehicle (Bev) and Hybrid Electric Vehicle (Hev)',NULL,'4932'),('49329','Other Land Transport Operation, N.e.c.',NULL,'4932'),('49331','Truck-for-hire Operation (With Driver)',NULL,'4933'),('49332','Freight Truck Operation',NULL,'4933'),('49333','Tank Truck Delivery Services',NULL,'4933'),('49339','Freight Transport Operation, by Road, N.e.c.',NULL,'4933'),('49400','Transport Via Pipeline ','This class includes transport of gases, liquids, water, slurry and other commodities via pipelines. It also includes operation of pump stations. This class excludes distribution of natural or manufactured gas, water or steam, see 3520,3530,3600; transport of water, liquids, etc, by trucks, see 4933.','4940'),('50111','Ocean Passenger Transport',NULL,'5011'),('50112','Interisland Water Passenger Transport',NULL,'5011'),('50113','Renting of Ship with Operator',NULL,'5011'),('50121','Ocean Freight Transport',NULL,'5012'),('50122','Interisland Water Freight Transport',NULL,'5012'),('50123','Towing and Pushing Services on Coastal and Trans-oceanic Waters',NULL,'5012'),('50210','Inland Passenger Water Transport ',' This class includes transport of passenger via rivers, canals, lakes and other inland waterways, including inside harbors and ports. It also includes rental of pleasure boats with crew for inland water transport.','5021'),('50220','Inland Freight Water Transport ',' This class includes transport of freight via rivers, canals, lakes and other inland waterways, including inside harbor and ports.','5022'),('51101','Domestic Air Passenger Transport',NULL,'5110'),('51102','International Air Passenger Transport',NULL,'5110'),('51103','Non-scheduled Air Passenger Transport',NULL,'5110'),('51201','Domestic Air-freight Transport',NULL,'5120'),('51202','International Air Freight Transport',NULL,'5120'),('51203','Non-scheduled Air Freight Transport',NULL,'5120'),('52101','General Bonded Warehouses Except Grain Warehouse',NULL,'5210'),('52102','Grain Warehouses',NULL,'5210'),('52103','Customs Bonded Warehouses',NULL,'5210'),('52104','Cold Storage',NULL,'5210'),('52109','Storage and Warehousing, N.e.c.',NULL,'5210'),('52211','Freight Terminal Facilities for Trucking Companies',NULL,'5221'),('52212','Operation of Parking Lots',NULL,'5221'),('52213','Operation of Toll Roads and Bridges',NULL,'5221'),('52219','Other Supporting Land Transport Activities, Including Towing Services and Truck Weighing Services, N.e.c.',NULL,'5221'),('52220','Service Activities Incidental to Water Transportation ',' This class includes : Activities related to water transport of passengers, animals or freight : operation of terminal facilities such as harbors and piers operation of waterway locks, etc navigation, pilotage and berthing activities lighterage, salvage activities lighthouse activities This class excludes : Cargo handling, see 5224; Operation of marinas, see 9329.','5222'),('52230','Service Activities Incidental to Air Transportation ',' This class includes : Activities related to air transport of passengers, animals or freight: operation of terminal facilities such as airway terminals, etc. airport and air-traffic-control activities ground service activities on airfields, etc. This class also includes firefighting and fire-prevention services at airports. This class excludes : Cargo handling, see 5224; Operation of flying schools, see 8559.','5223'),('52241','Containerized Cargo Handling,